data.description: Gorgeous Home. Covered Front Porch with composite decking. Brand new carpet. Whole house freshly (professionally) painted. Office/Flex room downstairs. Formal dining room. Massive yet cozy family room. Enormous Kitchen - Extra dining area - Large kitchen island with bar seating - granite counters. Upstairs loft can be used as 2nd family/playroom/game room or converted to a 4th bedroom. Luxury Primary with 2 walk-in closets, en-suite featuring separate soaking tub & shower. 2 car garage. Tankless water heater. Neighborhood offers pool, clubhouse, exercise room plus sidewalks everywhere. Low rate assumable loan, Sellers are experienced with the process and paperwork is ready to go.
